Raised%20by%20two%20accountants%20in%20Cali%2C%20Colombia%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20what%20a%20budget%20was%20since%20I%20was%20eight%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She%20continued%20her%20financial%20education%20as%20a%20university%20student.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20graduated%20as%20a%20finance%20professional%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20every%20strategy%20in%20the%20book%20on%20how%20to%20save%2C%20how%20to%20get%20out%20of%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rojas.%20That's%20why%20she%20was%20confused%20about%20her%20overspending%20habits%2C%20which%20started%20after%20landing%20her%20first%20job%20in%20Washington%20DC.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20studying%20and%20growing%20up%20knowing%20about%20money%2C%20why%20am%20I%20acting%20this%20way%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeeking%20answers%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20Google%20and%20fell%20into%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20money%20and%20psychology.%20The%20first%20resource%20she%20found%2C%20Morgan%20Housel's%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D74af18fd43fea8f26177251a9ec7986ea23e192eda85fd83e7099d48fcd06ca1%26postID%3D672542c7d057d3e5c5bfdca8%26postSlug%3Dmoney-coach-shares-top-book-recommendation-the-psychology-of-money-2024-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.barnesandnoble.com%252Fw%252Fthe-psychology-of-money-morgan-housel%252F1136394564%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Psychology%20of%20Money%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20one%20of%20her%20favorites.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20forces%20you%20to%20look%20at%20money%20through%20a%20different%20lens%20and%20consider%20the%20human%20behavior%20element%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20she%20felt%20was%20missing%20in%20traditional%20financial%20advice%3A%20%26quot%3BMany%20finance%20gurus%20that%20are%20out%20there%20tell%20you%2C%20'This%20is%20very%20simple%3A%20Don't%20spend%20and%20increase%20your%20revenues.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHousel%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20you%20understand%20how%20your%20emotions%20play%20out%20in%20things%20like%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20how%20you%20manage%20finances%2C%20and%20how%20you%20make%20financial%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20does%20a%20really%20good%20job%20of%20explaining%20that%20money%20is%20not%20just%20this%20plain%20and%20simple%20thing%3B%20it's%20complicated%20because%20there%20is%20a%20psychology%20behind%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERojas%2C%20who%20has%20since%20paid%20off%20her%20debt%2C%20earned%20her%20Trauma%20of%20Money%20certification%20and%20started%20her%20own%20financial%20education%20company%2C%20generally%20cautions%20against%20overly%20simplified%20or%20polarizing%20money%20advice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20black%20and%20white.%20It%20never%20is%20with%20money.%20It's%20understanding%20what%20works%20for%20you%20and%20what%20doesn't%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20same%20with%20money%20beliefs%20or%20money%20habits.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20perfect%20money%20habit%20or%20the%20worst%20money%20habit%20to%20have.%20There%20are%20money%20habits%20that%20work%20for%20you%20and%20your%20vision%2C%20and%20there%20are%20money%20habits%20that%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20vein%2C%20just%20because%20one%20strategy%20or%20behavioral%20change%20worked%20for%20someone%20else%2C%20doesn't%20mean%20it'll%20work%20for%20you.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%2C%20'If%20I%20did%20it%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it'%20doesn't%20work%20with%20money%2C%20because%20you%20leave%20the%20context%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20leave%20the%20context%20out%2C%20then%20you%20leave%20the%20human%20out%20%E2%80