0of%20three%20adult%20males%3C%2Fa%3E%20embedded%20in%20the%20rocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20were%20found%20in%20the%20gutters%20during%20the%20excavation%20process%20and%20were%20removed.%20They%20were%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flifelike-3d-animals-with-paint-cast-in-resin-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplicated%20using%20resin%20casts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rubber%2C%20applied%20in%20such%20a%20way%20as%20not%20to%20alter%20or%20damage%20the%20finds%20in%20any%20way%2C%20copied%20every%20minute%20detail%20of%20the%20burials%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20McDonald's%20Italia%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fmcdonalds-2000-year-old-skeletons-italy-1763778%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skeletons%20on%20display%20in%20the%20gallery%20are%20these%20recreated%20resin%20casts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAbove%20the%20glass%20floor%2C%20you're%20transported%20back%20to%20the%20present%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224353%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20order%20and%20payment%20kiosk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67238bef01ea6d83dee554c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223265%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20McDonald's%20in%20Frattocchie%20has%20a%20contemporary%20design.%20Pictured%20is%20another%20McDonald's%20that%20looks%20alike.%3Cp%3ESorbis%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20its%20section%20of%20glass%20floor%2C%20the%20restaurant%20resembles%20other%20McDonald's%20restaurants.%20It%20features%20e-kiosks%2C%20digital%20cash%20counters%2C%20a%20salad%20bar%2C%20and%20light%20wooden%20accents.%20It%20also%20offers%20different%20seating%20options%2C%20from%20family-friendly%20tables%20to%20bar%20stools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20McDonald's%20Italia%20told%20Newsweek%20th