n%20(the%20team%20in)%20a%20little%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20ridiculous%20(talk%20of%20rushing%20him%20in).%20How's%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20going%3F%20I%20could%20see%20his%20weaknesses%20before%20he%20went%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20successive%20Sheffield%20Shield%20hundreds%20for%20NSW%20against%20South%20Australia%20last%20month%2C%20Konstas'%20name%20was%20thrown%20up%20as%20a%20potential%20replacement%20for%20David%20Warner.%20The%20teenager%20then%20made%202%20and%2043%20against%20Victoria%20before%20a%20duck%20and%2016%20for%20Australia%20A%20against%20India%20A%20in%20Mackay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED'Costa%2C%20who%20started%20coaching%20aged%2019%2C%20is%20a%20Level%203%20coach%20with%20degrees%20in%20Sports%20Science%2C%20Sports%20Coaching%20and%20Psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20worked%20as%20the%20Vidharbha%20Cricket%20Association's%20Residential%20Academy%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730565420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjv9mscbo_prithvi-shaw_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhows-prithvi-shaw-going-australian-coach-takes-subtle-dig-at-india-star-while-talking-about-this-player-6926127%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22D'Costa%2C%20who%20was%20born%20to%20Anglo-Indian%20parents%20hailing%20from%20Chennai%2C%20has%20in%20the%20past%20coached%20Michael%20Clarke%2C%20the%20late%20Phillip%20Hughes%2C%20and%20helped%20Mitchell%20Starc%20switch%20to%20fast%20bowling%20from%20wicket-keeping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MAGA%20meltdown%20over%20Indians%20stealing%20jobs%20as%20racial%20abuse%20mounts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730565115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114888951%2Cimgsize-1688941.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%2