e%20without%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20this%20as%20another%20Canadian%20strategy%20to%20attack%20and%20malign%20India.%20Their%20senior%20officials%20have%20openly%20confessed%20that%20Canada%20is%20seeking%20to%20manipulate%20global%20opinions%20against%20India.%20As%20on%20other%20occasions%2C%20allegations%20are%20made%20repeatedly%20without%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20CANADA%20ALLEGED%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20most%20recent%20report%20about%20cyber%20security%2C%20titled%20'National%20Cyber%20Threat%20Assessment%202025-2026'%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20has%20called%20India%20a%20%26quot%3Bcyber%20adversary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%20it%20claimed%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20leadership%20almost%20certainly%20aspires%20to%20build%20a%20modernized%20cyber%20program%20with%20domestic%20cyber%20capabilities.%20India%20very%20likely%20uses%20its%20cyber%20program%20to%20advance%20its%20national%20security%20imperatives%2C%20including%20espionage%2C%20counter-terrorism%2C%20and%20the%20country's%20efforts%20to%20promote%20its%20global%20status%20and%20counter%20narratives%20against%20India%20and%20the%20Indian%20government.%20We%20assess%20that%20India's%20cyber%20program%20likely%20leverages%20commercial%20cyber%20vendors%20to%20enhance%20its%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3BWe%20assess%20that%20Indian%20state-sponsored%20cyber%20threat%20actors%20likely%20conduct%20cyber%20threat%20activity%20against%20Government%20of%20Canada%20networks%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20espionage.%20We%20judge%20that%20official%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%20will%20very%20likely%20drive%20Indian%20state-sponsored%20cyber%20threat%20activity%20against%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bcountries%20that%20aspire%20to%20become%20new%20centres%20of%20power%20within%20the%20global%20system%2C%20such%20as%20India%2C%20are%20building%20cyber%20programs%20that%20present%20varying%20levels%20of%20threat%20to%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20made%20these%20claims%20under%20'Section%201'%20of%20its%20cyber%20security%20report%20titled%20'Cyber%20Threat%20From%20State%20Adversaries'%20which%20it%20says%20%26quot%3Bintroduces%20the%20state%20cyber%20threat%20ecosystem%20and%20discusses%20the%20cyber%20threats%20to%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20enemy%20countries%20which%20include%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECANADA%20HARASSES%20INDIAN%20DIPLOMATIC%20STAFF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justin%20Trudeau-led%20Canada%20government%20has%20started%20violating%20all%20established%20international%20diplomatic%20norms%20in%20its%20hateful%20and%20spiteful%20pursuit%20to%20malign%20India%20in%20order%20to%20cater%20to%20its%20domestic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-canada-fallout-how-far-can-justin-trudeau-go-as-personal-electoral-gain-trumps-diplomatic-ties-6798226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolitical%20motives%20and%20objectives%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Diplomats%20and%20other%20Indian%20mission%20staff%20are%20being%20kept%20under%20round-the-clock%20surveillance%20and%20are%20even%20being%20intimidated%20routinely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20move%20that%20highlights%20its%20double-standards%2C%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20administration%2C%20which%20harps%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Brules-based%26quot%3B%20order%20has%20itself%20not%20been%20following%20any%20established%20rules%2C%20diplomatic%20norms%20and%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20today%20calle