quot%3BPhysically%20and%20mentally%2C%20running%20enables%20me%20to%20perform%20while%20I%20get%20little%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20me%20energy%20to%20do%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%2C%20and%20keeps%20me%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20listens%20to%20audiobooks%20during%20his%20runs%20to%20maintain%20his%20%26quot%3Bvoracious%26quot%3B%20reading%20habit%20and%20optimize%20his%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20has%20also%20connected%20him%20with%20like-minded%20individuals%2C%20because%20runners%20tend%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20people%20looking%20for%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20helped%20to%20educate%20him%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20healthy%20aging%20in%20communities%20of%20color.%20Spring%20Mountain%2C%20Ho's%20firm%2C%20backs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westharleminnovationnetwork.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWest%20Harlem%20Innovation%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20new%20businesses%20and%20entrepreneurial%20talent%20in%20the%20underserved%20NYC%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f4c4d83-3756-4ca4-9f4d-4a2bd5128f11%5C%22%3EHe%20tries%20to%20maintain%20other%20habits%20for%20longevity%20%E2%80%94%20apart%20from%20sleep%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20only%20gets%204.5%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-you-catch-up-on-sleep-experts-say-yes-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehours%20of%20sleep%20each%20night%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20research%20suggests%20is%20not%20beneficial%20for%20health.%20One%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosmedicine%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pmed.1004109%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20PLoS%20Medicine%20found%20that%20for%20adults%20over%2050%20years%20old%2C%20getting%20less%20than%20five%20hours%20of%20sleep%20a%20night%20can%20increase%20their%20risk%20of%20developing%20a%20chronic%20disease%20by%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bdesperately%20trying%20to%20get%20up%20to%20five%20hours%20a%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20in%20the%20meantime%20tries%20to%20practice%20other%20longevity-boosting%20habits%2C%20such%20as%20eating%20well%20and%20reducing%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20follows%20the%20%26quot%3Bbasics%26quot%3B%20of%20eating%20healthily%3A%20staying%20away%20from%20junk%20food%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-processed-foods-linked-early-death-study-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprocessed%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20managing%20his%20calorie%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20tries%20to%20minimize%20stress%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20in%20a%20high-pressure%20finance%20job.%20The%20environment%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20full%20of%20%26quot%3Bhigh-performing%20teams%20and%20high%20goals%2C%20so%20we're%20always%20stressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraining-tips-for-older-runners-from-72-year-old-marathoner-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730561341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723a49fa0a0cc14f2253e2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraining-tips-for-older-runners-from-72-year-old-marathoner-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20president%20of%20an%20NYC%20venture-capital%20firm%20wants%20to%20run%20100%20marathons%20by%20his%20100th%20birthday.%20He%20fits%20training%20into%20his%20busy%20schedule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22skenny%40businessinsider.com%20(Serafina%20Kenny)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraining-tips-for-older-runners-from-72-year-old-marathoner-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Promises%20Moon%2C%20Can't%20Deliver%26quot%3B%3A%20Hardeep%20Puri%20To%20NDTV%20On%20Guarantees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Congress-BJP%20war%20over%20guarantees%20and%20the%20comments%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Petroleum%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20has%20said%20the%20opposition%20party%20promises%20the%20Moon%2C%20but%20can't%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20drew%20a%20distinction%20between%20what%20he%20called%20the%20'freebie'%20model%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20'%3Cem%3Elabharthi%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(beneficiary)%20model%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20drives%20development.%20The%20minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20alleged%20Mysore%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(MUDA)%20scam%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20derogatory%20remark%20made%20by%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20MP%20against%20former%20BJP%20leader%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20who%20has%20now%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20led%20by%20the%20party's%20ally%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20statements%20by%20Mr%20Kharge%20and%20PM%20Modi%20over%20the%20Congress%20president%20reportedly%20pulling%20up%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20for%20his%20comments%20hinting%20at%20a%20review%20of%20one%20of%20the%20party's%20guarantees%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20governance%20model%20which%20is%20successful%2C%20which%20delivers%20economic%20growth%20and%20welfare%20to%20the%20people%20is%20a%20governance%20model.%20Any%20other%20model%2C%20which%20bases%20itself%20on%20freebies%2C%20or%20on%20empty%20promises%20not%20grounded%20in%20reality%2C%20is%20not%20a%20governance%20model.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20Mr%20Kharge%20over%20the%20use%20of%20terms%20like%20'betrayal'%20and%20'%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E'%20for%20the%20BJP%20government's%20guarantees%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader%20must%20have%20been%20excited%20when%20he%20got%20the%20post%20of%20party%20president%2C%20but%20is%20now%20discovering%20the%20downsides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20make%20promises%20on%20which%20you%20can't%20deliver.%20If%20you%20use%20words%20like%20review%2C%20it%20means%20you%20are%20not%20able%20to%20deliver.%20That%20is%20the%20hard%20truth.%20The%20Congress%20makes%20outlandish%20claims%20-%20it%20promises%20the%20Moon%2C%20and%20is%20not%20able%20to%20deliver%2C%20and%20then%20it%20gets%20caught.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20think%20in%20terms%20of%20imposing%20a%20tax%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20toilets%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20you%20are%20in%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Puri%20sneered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Writing%20On%20The%20Wall'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20that%20after%20the%20loss%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20seeing%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20is%20realising%20that%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ekhata-khat%2C%20phata-phat%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20model%20is%20failing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%20as%20prices%20are%20concerned%2C%20after%20all%20the%20bluff%2C%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20are%20still%20Rs%2010%20more%20expensive%20in%20Congress-ruled%20states%20than%20they%20are%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states.%20There%20is%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20the%20freebie%20models%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20the%20'%3Cem%3Elabharthis%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(beneficiaries)%20of%20a%20scheme%20like%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20and%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Puri%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Punjab%2C%20the%20AAP%20promised%20300%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20and%20families%20have%20two%20or%20three%20connections%20and%20rich%20people%20are%20misusing%20the%20scheme.%20Our%20model%20is%20that%20you%20come%20and%20get%20a%20solar%20panel%20from%20us%20at%20a%20reasonable%20cost.%20We%20will%20subsidise%20it%20a%20little%2C%20then%20you%20produce%20electricity.%20You%20can%20use%20300%20units%20for%20your%20consumption%20and%20the%20rest%20can%20be%20used%20for%20a%20charging%20station%20at%20your%20place%20or%20put%20back%20into%20the%20grid%20and%20earn%20some%20money.%20There's%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20giving%20somebody%20free%20fish%20to%20eat%20and%20teaching%20somebody%20how%20to%20fish%20so%20that%20he%20or%20she%20becomes%20a%20productive%20member%20of%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20he%20had%20responded%20to%20all%20seven%20points%20made%20by%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bbecoming%20a%20junior%20partner%20(in%20alliances)%20everywhere%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20Mr%20Kharge%20claiming%20that%20'Modi's%20guarantees'%2C%20which%20have%20been%20a%20key%20plank%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20have%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bcruel%20joke%26quot%3B%20on%20Indians%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said%20the%20joke%20is%20what%20the%20Congress%20is%20doing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi's%20guarantee%20carries%20weight.%20Modi's%20guarantee%20carries%20credibility.%20Whatever%20the%20party%20has%20said%20in%20all%20its%20election%20manifestos%20since%202014%2C%20it%20has%20delivered%20on%20each%20one%20of%20them.%20An%20additional%204%20crore%20houses%20are%20going%20to%20be%20built...%20on%20petrol%20prices%2C%20diesel%20prices%2C%20in%20all%20the%20PM's%20guarantees%2C%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20consumer%20is%20written%20in.%20In%20their%20model%2C%20they%20took%20an%20oil%20bond%20loan%20of%20Rs%201.41%20lakh%20crore%20and%20we%20are%20having%20to%20pay%20back%20Rs%203.2%20lakh%20crore.%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20honourable%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20is%20being%20delusional%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20over%20corruption%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20brought%20up%20the%20alleged%20MUDA%20scam%2C%20in%20which%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife%20was%20given%20prime%20plots%20of%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah's%20claim%20that%20the%20BJP%20left%20Karnataka%20plagued%20with%20%26quot%3B40%25%20commission%20corruption%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20government%20had%20inherited%20poor%20fiscal%20health%20from%20the%20previous%20BJP%20regime%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20minister%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20he%20also%20inherit%20the%20MUDA%20scheme%3F%20His%20wife%20got%20about%2015%20plots%2C%20did%20he%20also%20inherit%20that%3F%20They%20were%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20if%20there%20was%20any%20act%20of%20omission%20or%20commission%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20could%20have%20questioned%20it%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Congress)%20have%20been%20tainted%20by%20corruption%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time%20and%20when%20they%20have%20to%20answer%20questions%2C%20they%20start%20blaming%20each%20other.%20Now%20whether%20it%20is%20faultlines%20between%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20DK%20Shivakumar%20or%20both%20of%20them%20versus%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20I%20don't%20know.%20The%20Congress%20has%20to%20sort%20out%20this%20mess%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerogatory%20Remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20remark%20made%20by%20Arvind%20Sawant%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20against%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20who%20is%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20Mumbadevi%20Assembly%20constituency%20from%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20praised%20his%20former%20party%20colleague%20for%20making%20her%20voice%20heard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20kind%20of%20vocabulary%20is%20not%20acceptable%20anywhere.%20You%20don't%20refer%20to%20an%20opposition%20candidate%2C%20a%20woman%2C%20in%20those%20terms.%20Using%20a%20word%20like%20that%20is%20objectifying%20a%20candidate...%20I%20would%20like%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20my%20friends%20like%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20(an%20MP%20from%20Mr%20Sawant's%20party)%20or%20others%20whom%20I%20know%20quite%20well...%20they%20should%20stand%20up%20and%20condemn%20this%20comment.%20I%20think%20Shaina%20NC%20did%20very%20well%20in%20questioning%20it.%20Somebody%20told%20me%20that%20he%20has%20apologised%2C%20but%20I%20think%20this%20needs%20to%20be%20pursued%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion.%20And%20I'm%20sure%20that%20my%20sisters%20and%20daughters%20and%20our%20mothers%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20give%20an%20absolutely%20befitting%20reply%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20misogyny%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730560860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fn61ovlj8_hardeep-puri-interview_625x300_02_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-mallikarjun-kharge-congress-promises-moon-cant-deliver-hardeep-puri-to-ndtv-on-guarantees-6929458%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20Congress-BJP%20war%20over%20guarantees%20and%20the%20comments%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Petroleum%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20has%20said%20the%20opposition%20party%20promises%20the%20Moon%2C%20but%20can't%20deliver.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-mallikarjun-kharge-congress-promises-moon-cant-deliver-hardeep-puri-to-ndtv-on-guarantees-6929458%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22