m%2Fcricket%2F100-pain-free-mohammed-shami-wont-play-in-bengals-next-game-on-bccis-advice-report-reveals-6929317%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Investing%20legend%20Rob%20Arnott's%20%24147%20billion%20firm%20says%20stocks%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20have%20huge%20upside%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20is%20betting%20on%20these%207%20recent%20dropouts%20trading%20at%20bargain%20prices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20chart%20rally%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6716c56fa0a0cc14f222daee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Ewdstock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJust%20because%20a%20stock%20gets%20removed%20from%20an%20index%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20a%20bad%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERob%20Arnott's%20firm%20is%20betting%20on%20index%20deletions%20to%20deliver%20huge%20upside%20at%20low%20entry%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere%20are%207%20index%20rejects%20that%20have%20rebound%20potential.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20stock%20gets%20dropped%20from%20a%20major%20index%20like%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20index%20fund%20managers%20scramble%20to%20exit%20their%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20legendary%20investor%20and%20Research%20Affiliates%20founder%20and%20chairman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Frob-arnott%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERob%20Arnott%3C%2Fa%3E%20does%20the%20opposite%20%E2%80%94%20instead%2C%20he%20buys%20up%20index%20rejects%20at%20a%20deep%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20counterintuitive%20to%20bet%20on%20stocks%20that%20have%20performed%20so%20poorly%20that%20they've%20gotten%20kicked%20out%20of%20a%20major%20index%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20method%20to%20the%20madness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20can%20be%20delisted%20from%20an%20index%20for%20reasons%20such%20as%20insufficient%20market%20capitalization%2C%20bankruptcy%2C%20and%20noncompliance%20with%20exchange%20rules.%20Deletions%20often%20end%20up%20in%20the%20Russell%202000%20after%20falling%20out%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20or%20Russell%201000%20index.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20bad%20investments%2C%20according%20to%20Research%20Affiliates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnott%20and%20Forrest%20Henslee%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20research%20at%20Research%20Affiliates%2C%20found%20that%20in%20the%20year%20leading%20up%20to%20removal%2C%20index%20deletions%20typically%20lag%20the%20market%20by%20more%20than%20half.%20But%20after%20being%20deleted%2C%20it's%20a%20whole%20other%20story%3A%20in%20the%20five%20years%20after%20removal%2C%20index%20deletions%20outperform%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20by%2028%25%2C%20or%205%25%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Research%20Affiliates%20launched%20the%20Research%20Affiliates%20Deletions%20Index%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rafi.com%2Findex-strategies%2Fra-deletions-index-series%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENIXT%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20which%20creates%20an%20equally%20weighted%20portfolio%20of%20companies%20deleted%20from%20a%20top%20500%20and%20top%201000%20index.%20Stocks%20are%20held%20for%20a%20five-year%20period%20with%20annual%20rebalancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227106877a-36ce-4d4c-8fac-ec267fefffb4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20cheap%20way%20to%20lean%20into%20small%20and%20mid-cap%20value%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20deletions%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20exposure%20to%20stocks%20outside%20the%20large-cap%20universe.%20Deletions%20are%20priced%20cheaply%2C%20and%20usually%2C%20if%20they've%20fallen%20out%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20territory%2C%20they%20have%20relatively%20small%20market%20caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Arnott%20and%20Henslee%2C%20index%20deletions%20are%20priced%20at%20an%20extreme%20discount%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20half%20of%20the%20market%20multiple%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20these%20companies%20to%20appreciate%20in%20price.%20Meanwhile%2C%20new%20index%20additions%20are%20priced%20at%20roughly%20twice%20the%20market%20multiple%2C%20creating%20a%20widespread.%20These%20deletions'%20low%20valuations%20might%20not%20be%20aligned%20with%20their%20intrinsic%20value%2C%20meaning%20investors%20gain%20when%20valuations%20normalize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20when%20a%20stock%20is%20removed%20from%20an%20index%2C%20index%20fund%20managers%20need%20to%20rebalance%20their%20portfolios%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20rapid%20sell-off%20of%20the%20deleted%20stocks.%20High%20levels%20of%20selling%20activity%20depress%20the%20stock%20prices%20of%20index%20deletions%20even%20further%2C%20creating%20an%20even%20bigger%20opportunity%20for%20these%20stocks%20to%20bounce%20back%2C%20according%20to%20Arnott%20and%20Henslee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20investing%20strategy%20is%20especially%20advantageous%20in%20the%20current%20growth-dominated%20market.%20Big%20Tech%20stocks%20have%20carried%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20to%20record%20high%20after%20record%20high%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bdeletions%20may%20well%20add%20abnormal%20upside%20to%20a%20portfolio%20when%20the%20current%20growth-dominated%20bubble%20(and%2C%20yes%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bubble)%20starts%20to%20deflate%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnott%20and%20Henslee%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Q3%20earnings%20season%20continues%2C%20the%20market%20has%20come%20to%20be%20disproportionately%20impacted%20by%20the%20results%20of%20a%20few%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20biggest%20companies.%20Nvidia%20earnings%20releases%20have%20become%20a%20major%20economic%20event%20almost%20akin%20to%20a%20FOMC%20meeting%2C%20in%20Henslee's%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20buy%20a%20company%20that's%20highly%20valued%2C%20that%20company%20needs%20to%20perform%20spectacularly%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20its%20high%20valuation%2C%26quot%3B%20Henslee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20deletions%2C%20the%20opposite%20is%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20companies%20are%20not%20overvalued%2C%20and%20they're%20actually%20priced%20for%20the%20worst%2C%26quot%3B%20Henslee%20said%20of%20deletions.%20%26quot%3BAll%20they%20need%20to%20do%20is%20outperform%20bleak%20expectations%20to%20provide%20a%20good%20return%20on%20your%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8ddb0d9-b752-4407-8f32-05898ca5d1b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E7%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20dropouts%20to%20monitor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20index-beating%20returns%2C%20you%20can't%20invest%20blindly%20in%20any%20stock%20that's%20been%20kicked%20out%20of%20an%20index%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20these%20companies%20do%20rebound%2C%20some%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Henslee%20said.%20%26quot%3BYour%20winners%20need%20to%20make%20up%20for%20your%20losers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20Affiliates%20screens%20index%20deletions%20based%20on%20quality%20to%20avoid%20so-called%20falling%20knives%2C%20or%20stocks%20that%20are%20plummeting%20in%20price%20with%20no%20sign%20of%20a%20turnaround.%20But%20in%20the%20aggregate%2C%20a%20portfolio%20of%20deletions%20should%20outperform%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20after%20being%20removed%20from%20the%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EListed%20below%20are%20some%20of%20the%20top%20constituents%20of%20Research%20Affiliates'%20deletions%20index%20that%20have%20recently%20been%20removed%20from%20major%20indexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5CnLumen%20Technologies%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22815%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lumen%20one%20year%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723925d01ea6d83dee557b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20