y)%20leader%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20defended%20the%20statement%2C%20claiming%20the%20candidate%20from%20Mumbadevi%20had%20come%20from%20outside%20and%20was%20thus%20'imported'.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Shaina%20NC%20had%20switched%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Shaina%20NC%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BArvind%20Sawant%20called%20me%20'imported%20%3Cem%3Emaal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(goods)'%20and%20the%20Mumbadevi%20MLA%2C%20Amin%20Patel%2C%20was%20smiling.%20Would%20Amin%20Patel%20have%20made%20this%20remark%20for%20his%20sister%20or%20wife%3F%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20the%20Uddhav%20Sena%20about%20Sanjay%20Raut's%20statement%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20apologise%20because%20I%20am%20imported.%20My%20family%20has%20been%20working%20in%20South%20Mumbai%20for%20three%20generations%2C%20I%20have%20also%20shown%20proof%20that%20I%20campaigned%20for%20Arvind%20Sawant%20between%202014%20and%202019.%20I%20was%20your%20'Ladki%20Bahin'%20then%20and%20have%20become%20'imported%20%3Cem%3Emaal%3C%2Fem%3E'%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Raut%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20any%20objection%20to%20words%20like%20%3Cem%3E'maal'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20shows%20your%20mentality.%20It%20is%20surprising%20that%20Mr%20Sawant%20apologised%20after%2030%20hours%20but%20Mr%20Raut%20is%20saying%20nothing%20wrong%20was%20said.%20So%2C%20what%20is%20the%20official%20stand%20of%20the%20'Maha%20Vinash%20Aghadi'%20(a%20play%20on%20the%20opposition%20coalition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi)%3F%20What%20is%20the%20stand%20of%20Congress%20Maharashtra%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%2C%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20President%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20President%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaina%20NC%20said%20with%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20due%20on%20November%2020%2C%20discussions%20should%20be%20about%20the%20work%20that%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20apology%20was%20made%20after%20a%20case%20was%20registered.%20Using%20the%20word%20%3Cem%3E'maal'%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20objectification%20and%20it%20means%20that%20I%20am%20someone's%20property%2C%20which%20I%20am%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaina%20NC%20said%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20list%20schemes%20like%20'Ladki%20Bahin'%20introduced%20for%20women%20under%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Arvind%20Sawant%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20giving%20women%20their%20due%20respect.%20My%20remarks%20were%20distorted%20and%20I%20was%20deliberately%20targeted.%20This%20hurt%20me.%20Still%2C%20if%20my%20comments%20hurt%20anybody's%20sentiments%2C%20I%20regret%20them%20and%20apologise.%20In%20my%2055%20years%20of%20public%20life%2C%20I%20have%20never%20insulted%20women%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Raut%2C%20however%2C%20defended%20the%20remark.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20no%20insult.%20Arvind%20Sawant%20is%20our%20senior%20MP.%20He%20just%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Mumbadevi%20(Shaina%20NC)%20has%20come%20from%20outside...%20If%20she%20is%20an%20'imported%20maal'%2C%20how%20is%20this%20an%20insult%20to%20women...%20What%20did%20you%20say%20about%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%3F%20You%20should%20go%20through%20history%20once...If%20a%20person%20from%20outside%20contests%20elections%2C%20people%20say%20that%20they%20have%20come%20from%20outside...There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20create%20such%20a%20big%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730551800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Ftdg7beog_shaina-nc_625x300_04_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-sawant-import