test-with-canadian-government-after-modis-right-hand-man-linked-to-violent-criminal-activity-13246562%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHarassment%2C%20Intimidation%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20On%20Surveillance%20Of%20Officials%20In%20Canada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20its%20ties%20with%20Canada%20continued%20to%20remain%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20India%20on%20Saturday%20said%20some%20of%20its%20consular%20officials%20were%20informed%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20that%20they%20have%20been%20under%20audio%20and%20video%20surveillance%2C%20and%20termed%20the%20action%20a%20%26quot%3Bflagrant%20violation%26quot%3B%20of%20diplomatic%20conventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20Canada%20could%20not%20hide%20behind%20technicalities%20to%20justify%20its%20harassment%20and%20intimidation%2C%20India%20said%20it%20had%20lodged%20a%20protest%20with%20the%20Canadian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20briefing%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20consular%20officials%20were%20recently%20informed%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20that%20they%20have%20been%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20under%20audio%20and%20video%20surveillance.%20Their%20communications%20have%20also%20been%20intercepted.%20We%20have%20formally%20protested%20to%20the%20Canadian%20government%20as%20we%20deem%20these%20actions%20to%20be%20a%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20relevant%20diplomatic%20and%20consular%20conventions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20India's%20diplomatic%20and%20consular%20personnel%20are%20already%20functioning%20in%20an%20environment%20of%20%26quot%3Bextremism%20and%20violence%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20citing%20technicalities%2C%20the%20Canadian%20Government%20cannot%20justify%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20indulging%20in%20harassment%20and%20intimidation...%20This%20action%20of%20the%20Canadian%20government%20aggravates%20the%20situation%20and%20is%20incompatible%20with%20established%20diplomatic%20norms%20and%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20briefing%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20also%20revealed%20that%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20had%20been%20summoned%20on%20Friday%20over%20claims%20by%20Canada's%20Deputy%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Minister%20David%20Morrison%20that%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20ordered%20the%20targeting%20of%20Khalistani%20extremists%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20a%20diplomatic%20note%20had%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20Canadian%20High%20Commission%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20conveyed%20in%20the%20note%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20protests%20in%20the%20strongest%20terms%20to%20the%20absurd%20and%20baseless%20references%20made%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20of%20India%20before%20the%20committee%20by%20Deputy%20Minister%20David%20Morrison.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20reports%20of%20Canada%20admitting%20that%20its%20officials%20leaked%20sensitive%20information%20to%20the%20Washington%20Post%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20such%20actions%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bserious%20consequences%26quot%3B%20for%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20revelation%20that%20high%20Canadian%20officials%20deliberately%20leak%20unfounded%20insinuations%20to%20the%20international%20media%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conscious%20strategy%20to%20discredit%20India%20and%20influence%20other%20nations%20only%20confirms%20the%20view%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20long%20held%20about%20the%20current%20Canadian%20government's%20political%20agenda%20and%20behavioural%20pattern.%20Such%20irresponsible%20actions%20will%20have%20serious%20consequences%20for%20bilateral%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20been%20strained%20since%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20claimed%20-%20without%20offering%20any%20evidence%20-%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3BIndian%20agents%26quot%3B%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20The%20allegation%20has%20been%20rubbished%20by%20New%20Delhi%20several%20times%20and%20it%20has%20asked%20Canada%20to%20produce%20evidence%20to%20back%20up%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20hit%20a%20new%20low%20earlier%20this%20month%20when%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20was%20termed%20a%20%26quot%3Bperson%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20killing.%20India%20dismissed%20the%20fresh%20charge%20as%20%26quot%3Bludicrous%26quot%3B%20and%20withdrew%20the%20High%20Commissioner%20and%20some%20diplomats%20while%20expelling%20six%20Canadian%20officials%2C%20including%20Canada's%20acting%20High%20Commissioner%20Stewart%20Ross%20Wheeler.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730551020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fpm-modi-justin-trudeau-pti_650x400_61519877647.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-canada-india-canada-ties-harassment-intimidation-india-on-surveillance-of-officials-in-canada-6928387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20its%20ties%20with%20Canada%20continued%20to%20remain%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20India%20on%20Saturday%20said%20some%20of%20its%20consular%20officials%20were%20informed%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20that%20they%20have%20been%20under%20audio%20and%20video%20surveillance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-canada-india-canada-ties-harassment-intimidation-india-on-surveillance-of-officials-in-canada-6928387%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Friends%20Of%20Army%20Officer%2C%20Killed%20In%20Action%2C%20Send%2