er%20and%20advisor%2C%20holds%20an%20engineering%20degree%20and%20an%20MBA%20from%20IIM%20Calcutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20a%20game%20of%20tennis%20that%20the%20three%20decided%20to%20establish%20TCF!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20the%20school%20experience%20with%20enhanced%20facilities%20and%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20the%20foundation%20did%20after%20adopting%20the%20school%20was%20create%20a%20better%20environment%20for%20the%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20revamped%20the%20classrooms%20and%20built%20a%20library%2C%20toilet%2C%20garden%2C%20and%20computer%20laboratory.%20We%20made%20it%20a%20nicer%20place%20for%20the%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20enhance%20learning%20and%20adopt%20different%20methodologies%20of%20teaching%2C%20they%20appointed%20an%20academic%20director%2C%20Akhila%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20along%20with%20eight%20qualified%20teachers%20and%20volunteers.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20children%20began%20to%20enjoy%20their%20classes%20more.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20maintain%20a%201%3A10%20teacher-to-student%20ratio%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T192700.815-173