20to%20ensure%20accuracy.%20Currently%2C%20the%20team%20sends%20photographers%20to%20supermarkets%20to%20capture%20product%20images%20and%20ingredient%20labels%20directly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20rely%20on%20internet%20data%20for%20about%2020%25%20of%20our%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20clarifies.%20Essentially%2C%20they%20crowdsource%20product%20images%20and%20information%20to%20verify%20product%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECombating%20misleading%20labels%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruthIn%E2%80%99s%20assessments%20extend%20beyond%20nutritional%20profiles.%20Their%20algorithm%20evaluates%20several%20factors%3A%2045%25%20is%20based%20on%20the%20nutritional%20profile%2C%2045%25%20on%20the%20health%20impact%20of%20ingredients%2C%20and%2010%25%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20adhere%20to%20ICMR%20and%20NIN%20standards%20set%20by%20dietitians%20and%20nutritionists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20algorithm%20interprets%20product%20images%2C%20extracting%20and%20manually%20verifying%20information%20before%20assigning%20a%20health%20rating.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20penalise%20products%20for%20adding%20known%20harmful%20additives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnhealthy%20diets%2C%20alongside%20physical%20inactivity%2C%20tobacco%20and%20alcohol%20use%2C%20and%20air%20pollution%2C%20remain%20major%20contributors%20to%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs).%20A%20report%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20reveals%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20deaths%20from%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs)%20in%20India%20rose%20significantly%2C%20from%2037.9%25%20in%201990%20to%2061.8%25%20in%202016%2C%20with%20cardiovascular%20diseases%2C%20chronic%20respiratory%20diseases%2C%20cancers%2C%20and%20diabetes%20being%20the%20leading%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20these%20rising%20concerns%20that%20TruthIn%20hopes%20to%20address.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20talk%20about%20potato%20chips%2C%20you%20might%20think%20they%E2%80%99re%20bad%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20fried%20in%20oil%20and%20salt%2C%20but%20they%20often%20contain%20many%20other%20additives%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20or%20understand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20the%20team%20remains%20committed%20to%20their%20goal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20approach%20this%20from%20a%20solution-based%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20food.%20Our%20mission%20is%20to%20educate%20and%20empower%20consumers.%E2%80%9D%20The%20TruthIn%20team%20consists%20of%2035%20members%2C%20including%2015%20nutritionists%20and%20doctors%2C%20working%20alongside%20tech%20professionals.%20The%20initiative%20is%20entirely%20bootstrapped%20and%20self-funded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20TruthIn%20has%20an%20active%20user%20base%20of%20approximately%2085%2C000%20to%201%2C00%2C000%20users%20each%20month.%20The%20app%20features%20a%20unique%20TruthIn%20Rating%20system%20that%20assigns%20health%20impact%20of%20food%20products.%20Products%20are%20assigned%20health%20ratings%20on%20a%20scale%20from%201%20to%205%2C%20with%205%20being%20the%20healthiest%20option.%20Users%20can%20easily%20find%20products%20that%20match%20their%20dietary%20needs%20and%20preferences%20through%20filter%20tags%20for%20nutrients%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20allergens.%20The%20Shopping%20Cart%20Insights%20makes%20the%20shopping%20experience%20better%20by%20giving%20intelligent%20insights%20on%20cart%20contents%2C%20ensuring%20all%20products%20meet%20health%20criteria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20simply%20scanning%20the%20barcode%20on%20a%20product%E2%80%99s%20packaging%2C%20users%20can%20get%20detailed%20information%20about%20its%20rating%20and%20relevant%20tags%2C%20such%20as%20high%20sodium%2C%20fat%2C%20sugar%20content%2C%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20and%20sources%20of%20fibre%20or%20protein.%20Additionally%2C%20TruthIn%20is%20building%20a%20depository%20of%20products%20for%20users%20to%20check%20specific%20product%20information%20without%20scanning.%20With%20a%20subscription%2C%20users%20can%20also%20get%20personalised%20dietary%20insights%20through%20the%20MatchMeter%20feature%2C%20which%20considers%20age%2C%20gender%2C%20health%20conditions%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20TruthIn%20announced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350012%2Frevant-himatsingka-food-pharmer-nutrition-ingredient-list-read-label-padhega-india-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevant%20Himatsingka%2C%20popular%20as%20Foodpharmer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20their%20brand%20ambassador.%20%E2%80%9CRevant%20and%20our%20journey%20kind%20of%20began%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20I%20was%20really%20impressed%20that%20one%20single%20person%20has%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20this%20so%20openly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20shares.%20Together%2C%20they%20aim%20to%20tackle%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20complex%20product%20labels%20an