Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-28-at-19.40.08-min-1730124705.jpeg%3Fresize%3D1024%252C1536%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-28-at-19.40.08-min-1730124705.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C225%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-28-at-19.40.08-min-1730124705.jpeg%3Fw%3D1067%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201067w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372709%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENikhil%20Taneja%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20quite%20aggressive%20during%20my%20first%20session.%20I%20carried%20a%20lot%20of%20masculine%20energy%20and%20was%20unsure%20of%20how%20therapy%20would%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20was%20soon%20diagnosed%20with%20clinical%20anxiety%20and%20gradually%20realised%20that%20seeking%20help%20was%20okay.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20way%20out.%20I%20understood%20that%20this%20is%20real%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20fighting%20it%2C%20I%20accepted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202017%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20quit%20YRF.%20%E2%80%9CI%20owed%20it%20to%20myself.%E2%80%9D%20He%20acknowledges%20his%20privilege%20in%20being%20able%20to%20do%20so%2C%20as%20his%20wife%20was%20working%20at%20the%20time%20and%20he%20had%20savings%20to%20fall%20back%20on.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERedefining%20masculinity%3A%20%E2%80%98Be%20a%20man%2C%20%3Cem%3Eyaar%3C%2Fem%3E!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20returned%20home%20to%20his%20parents%20in%20Bahrain%20and%20spent%20time%20with%20loved%20ones.%20He%20engaged%20in%20activities%20he%20loved%20%E2%80%94%20travelling%2C%20reconnecting%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20reigniting%20lost%20connections.%20He%20changed%20his%20phone%20number%20and%20effectively%20switched%20off%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20biggest%20learnings%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20breaking%20free%20from%20the%20societal%20definitions%20of%20masculinity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20reflects%20the%20conditioning%20of%20masculinity%20that%20many%20boys%20in%20our%20country%20experience.%20Everything%20is%20linked%20to%20money%20and%20providing.%20We%20never%20take%20time%20to%20find%20joy%20in%20life.%20Historically%2C%20men%20have%20been%20viewed%20as%20providers%20and%20women%20are%20seen%20as%20nurturers.%20Today%2C%20while%20women%20play%20both%20roles%2C%20men%20are%20still%20not%20encouraged%20to%20embrace%20their%20nurturing%20side.%20We%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20burden%20of%20patriarchy%20on%20men%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20expresses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20wanted%20to%20break%20out%20of%20the%20cycle%20where%20one%20looks%20at%20happiness%20as%20a%20destination.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20recognise%20your%20worth%20as%20a%20human%20being.%20You%20owe%20it%20to%20yourself%20to%20celebrate%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20how%2C%20as%20children%2C%20our%20parents%20promised%20to%20buy%20us%20video%20games%20or%20new%20phones%20or%20toys%20if%20we%20scored%20well%20in%20exams%2C%20Nikhil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20carry%20this%20conditioning%20as%20adults%2C%20leading%20to%20rewarding%20ourselves%20on%20every%20academic%20or%20professional%20achievement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherapy%20helped%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%20unlearn%20and%20understand%20himself%20on%20a%20deeper%20level.%20During%20his%20eight-month%20break%2C%20Nikhil%20sought%20to%20find%20purpose%20in%20life.%20He%20loved%20teaching%20and%20interacting%20with%20young%20people%2C%20while%20his%20skills%20lay%20in%20entertainment%20and%20writing.%20How%20could%20he%20combine%20the%20two%20to%20create%20a%20tangible%20impact%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20youngsters%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pursuit%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20Yuvaa%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYuvaa%20is%20a%20purpose-driven%20youth%20media%2C%20research%2C%20and%20impact%20organisation%20that%20hopes%20to%20start%20meaningful%20conversations%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20youth%2C%20particularly%20Gen%20Z.%20We%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20young%20people%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20who%20are%20feeling%20lonely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20began%20with%20a%20roadshow%2C%20travelling%20to%20150%20campuses%20in%2035%20cities%20over%20nine%20months.%20The%20idea%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20to%20talk%20about%20mental%20health%20and%20sexual%20health%2C%20providing%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20young%20people%20to%20share%20their%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20roadshow%2C%20Nikhil%20encountered%20many%20young%20boys%20whose%20stories%20moved%20him%20deeply.%20%E2%80%9CAn%2018-year-old%20boy%20told%20me%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20told%20him%20%E2%80%98I%20love%20you.%E2%80%99%20Another%20teen%20shared%20that%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20hugged%20him.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20intimacy%20to%20our%20boys%20and%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eokay%20to%20express%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20provide%20a%20space%20to%20all%20the%20boys%20and%20girls%20in%20our%20country%20by%20creating%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20Nikhil%20started%20a%20show%20called%20%3Cem%3EBe%20a%20Man%2C%20Yaar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20male%20celebrities%20such%20as%20Javed%20Akhtar%2C%20Gajraj%20Rao%2C%20Boman%20Irani%2C%20Vicky%20Kaushal%2C%20Karan%20Johar%2C%20Bhuvan%20Bam%2C%20and%20Zakir%20Khan.%20The%20show%20promotes%20honest%2C%20vulnerable%20conversations%20where%20men%20talk%20about%20their%20feelings%20and%20mental%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzT1CUdo1-B%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzT1CUdo1-B%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzT1CUdo1-B%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Yuvaa%20(%40weareyuvaa)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20boy%20sees%20his%20favourite%20celebrity%20being%20open%20and%20vulnerable%2C%20he%20will%20realise%20that%20he%20too%20can%20share%20his%20feelings.%20Modern%20masculinity%20is%20about%20embracing%20yourselves%20and%20accepting%20who%20you%20are%2C%20rather%20than%20conforming%20to%20what%20the%20world%20expects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20has%20been%20a%20hit%2C%20igniting%20important%20conversations%20around%20men%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20masculinity.%20As%20Javed%20Akhtar%20poignantly%20stated%20on%20the%20show%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20angry%20young%20man%20is%20not%20just%20angry%2C%20he%20is%20deeply%20hurt.%20%3Cem%3EMard%20ko%20dard%20kyun%20nahi%20hota%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BWhy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20a%20man%20feel%20hurt%3F%5D%20Is%20there%20some%20problem%3F%20%3Cem%3EHona%20chahiye%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BHe%20should%20feel%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20hopes%20that%20through%20the%20show%2C%20we%20learn%20to%20embrace%20and%20accept%20ourselves.%20He%20has%20a%20message%20for%20every%20young%20person%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20identify%20as%20male%2C%20female%2C%20or%20queer%3A%20%E2%80%9CMake%20money%2C%20but%20also%20make%20time%20for%20yourself.%20Be%20kind%20to%20yourself.%20All%20that%20matters%20is%20a%20good%20family%20and%20friend%20circle%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20great%20memories.%20Maximise%20your%20time%20with%20your%20loved%20ones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20my%20favourite%20episodes%20from%20the%20series%20%3Cem%3EBe%20A%20Man%2C%20Yaar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20actor%20Imran%20Khan%20candidly%20shared%20his%20struggles%20with%20mental%20health.%20Discussing%20the%20stigma%20around%20therapy%2C%20he%20remarked%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20looked%20down%20upon%20to%20%E2%80%9Clie%20down%20on%20a%20couch%20and%20talk%20about%20feelings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20you%20respect%20a%20man%20who%20is%20not%20earning%3F%20How%20do%20you%20respect%20a%20man%20who%20is%20not%20getting%20up%20and%20going%20to%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20we%20start%20respecting%20men%20who%20embrace%20their%20weaknesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nikhil%20Taneja%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730126019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-28-at-19.40.08-min-1730124705.jpeg%3Fw%3D1067%26quality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D372684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikhil%20Taneja%2C%20founder%20of%20Yuvaa%2C%20a%20youth%20media%20company%2C%20went%20through%20a%20period%20of%20great%20anxiety%20when%20he%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20his%20career.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20look%20at%20what%20success%20really%20means%2C%20breaking%20out%20of%20the%20definitions%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20man%2C%20and%20the%20roles%20defined%20by%20society.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F372684%2Fnikhil-taneja-yuvaa-mens-mental-health-advocate-yuvaa-clinical-anxiety-yrf-producer-writer-be-a-man%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Transforming%20Lives%3A%20How%20a%20Mumbai-Based%20Initiative%20Has%20Delivered%20Quality%20Healthcare%20Since%201968%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EL%26amp%3BT%20Health%20Centre%2C%20Andheri%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Tukaram%20Pawar%20(73)%20is%20eager%20for%20his%20appointment%20slated%20for%20this%20afternoon%20with%20his%20physician%2C%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20Dr%20Alaka%20Deshpande.%20It%20is%20a%20weekday%2C%20but%20the%20OPD%20%E2%80%94%20where%20Pawar%20is%20waiting%20with%20the%20other%20patients%2C%20also%20here%20to%20see%20Dr%20Deshpande%20%E2%80%94%20is%20filled%20to%20capacity.%20He%20takes%20advantage%20of%20the%20wait%20to%20explain%20his%20enthusiasm.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20sugar%20levels%20are%20in%2