corner%20of%20the%20country%20you%20are%20in.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20lose%20their%20child%20like%20my%20parents%20did%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabynama%20also%20plans%20to%20make%20its%20services%20more%20affordable%2C%20aiming%20to%20reach%20all%20sections%20of%20society.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20AI%20(Artificial%20Intelligence)%2C%20they%20are%20building%20a%20chatbot%20on%20their%20app%2C%20which%20will%20have%20answers%20to%20common%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20can%20simply%20download%20the%20app%2C%20ask%20a%20question%2C%20and%20get%20an%20answer.%20In%20case%20they%20need%20further%20assistance%2C%20they%20can%20book%20a%20consultation.%20We%20are%20planning%20to%20launch%20plans%20starting%20from%20Rs%2099%20per%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Sumitra%2C%20the%20most%20satisfying%20part%20has%20been%20helping%20parents.%20She%20recounts%20her%20first%20call%2C%20where%20she%20diagnosed%20a%20child%20with%20autism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20call%20was%20from%20a%20parent%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20an%20MBBS%20student%20who%20felt%20something%20was%20wrong%20with%20his%20child%2C%20but%20consultations%20with%20eight%20doctors%20had%20led%20nowhere.%20A%20few%20questions%20in%2C%20I%20realised%20the%20baby%20was%20autistic%20and%20advised%20him%20to%20start%20therapy.%20He%20soon%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20since%20therapy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20available%20in%20his%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20later%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20tears%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20she%20called%20me%20an%20angel.%20Her%20child%20was%20now%20thriving%20and%20interacting%20with%20other%20kids.%20There%20was%20a%20stark%20improvement%20in%20him%20after%20therapy.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20days%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%2